Event Title: General Election Afternoon Canvassing in Bexleyheath 14th June 2024
Description:
Join us for a canvassing session in Bexleyheath, where we will be talking to voters about local issues and campaigning for the upcoming General Election to help us win this seat. Don't worry if you have not been out before, you will be paired with an experienced canvasser.

We recommend you bring a smartphone with data as we use the Labour Doorstep App. Please pre-login to https://doorstep.labour.org.uk and activate your account in advance. You'll be asked for a Passcode and Pin which will be supplied at the meeting point. Don't worry if you can't get this set up, you can still come along!
Creator: Nathan Ogunleye
